==Ancient Greek==

===Etymology===
A primary verb

===Pronunciation===
δέω / deō / deh'-o

===Verb===
'''δέω'''

# to [[bind]] (in various applications, literally or figuratively): - bind, be in bonds, knit, tie, wind. 

